rComments: The lectures are short and basic BSA the homeworks and tests are 5 levels higher in difficulties which is very frustrating as you have been tested for something you have not been thought or been explained a problem

This class has probably been the hardest one I have taken so far, the professor gives you a quiz almost every week and although they're not easy if you prepare for it you'll do well. At first I found it very hard but if you dedicate yourself to prepare for quizzes, do the group assignment, the online hwk. and prepare for the final, you'll do well.
